data.description: Welcome to 1036 S Avenida del Oro W, an enchanting adobe-style residence nestled in the heart of Pueblo West, Colorado. Each day, sweeping mountain vistas invite you to embrace tranquility and natural beauty. This delightful 4-bedroom home harmonizes spacious layout with southwestern flair. The main level hosts a generously-sized primary bedroom suite with large bathroom and walk-in closet, an additional cozy bedroom, and another full bathroom. A dining room adjacent to the living room offers elegant space for entertaining, while a mudroom/laundry room off the two-car garage adds practicality. The spacious kitchen has ample storage including built-in pantry shelves and stainless appliances. Descend to the fully-finished basement featuring two additional bedrooms, a full bath, several storage rooms, and a pool table that stays with the house. Ample storage space provides endless possibilities for guest accommodations, hobbies, or entertainment. Nestled on a sprawling 1.2-acre lot, enjoy unparalleled privacy amidst picturesque surroundings. Host outdoor gatherings on the covered front porch or relax in the shade of the covered back porch. A storage shed offers additional space for outdoor essentials.
